q {
Q:"Three G.M between 5 and 0.008 are:"
A:"c"
O:a) "0.2, 0.5, 0.6", b) "0.02, 0.05, 0.06", c) "1.0, 0.2, 0.04", d) "None"
R:"Let terms be \\(5, ar, ar^2, ar^3, 0.008\\). \\(ar^4 = 0.008 \\Rightarrow 5r^4 = 0.008 \\Rightarrow r^4 = 0.0016 \\Rightarrow r = 0.2\\). The G.Ms are \\(5(0.2)=1\\), \\(1(0.2)=0.2\\), \\(0.2(0.2)=0.04\\)."
}

